results.abstract: Khrushchev appearance on motion-picture screen applauded in Cuba during showing of documentary on Bolshevik Revolution anniv; Amb Alekseyev does not applaud

headline.main: Cuban Officials Applaud Khrushchev on Screen

results.snippet: HAVANA, Nov. 6 -- Nikita S. Khrushchev's appearance on a motion-picture screen produced a salvo of applause today from a largely official Cuban audience.

byline.original: Special to The New York Times

results.lead_paragraph: HAVANA, Nov. 6 -- Nikita S. Khrushchev's appearance on a motion-picture screen produced a salvo of applause today from a largely official Cuban audience.
